SIMD Module Stability Marker
============================

Version: 1.0.0-stable
Date: 2025-12-27
Status: FROZEN

This marker file indicates that the fafafa.core.simd module has been
audited and verified as production-ready.

STABILITY GUARANTEES
--------------------
1. API Stability: Public API will remain backward compatible
2. ABI Stability: TSimdDispatchTable structure will not change
3. Behavior Stability: Same inputs produce same outputs

MODIFICATION POLICY
-------------------
Before modifying any file in the SIMD module:

1. Run full test suite: bash tests/run_all_tests.sh fafafa.core.simd
2. Ensure all 439 tests pass
3. Verify zero memory leaks
4. Update SIMD_STABILITY_REPORT.md if behavior changes
5. Increment version number for breaking changes

